snippet.title: Pursuit of Wonder
snippet.description:
Content that makes you curious, inspired, and feel good. 

Wonder is the feeling of curiosity and/or appreciation inspired by something that is beautiful or unfamiliar.  At Pursuit of Wonder, we produce content with the goal of creating that feeling. 

We cover a wide range of topics related to things like social, emotional, and intellectual wellbeing, with a variety of formats including video essays, short stories, guided experiences, and much more.

For inquiries, email at: pursuit.wonder.media@gmail.com
